settings.description: Honestly loosely based on one level from the SMBX game 'the invasion 2', for remember a level with the hammer bros themes and mario bros elements? well... here I'm trying to go for that theme!
Get through the airship and beat big boo, also giant cannonball is angry sun idk why it is but idc I think its funny. Also he forgot the other boos and has fire snakes, enjoy this level lmao.
Mario uses the backdoor of Luigi's castle to destroy Luigi in one of the bowser suits (bowser suits are robots) also final bowser fight looking cool ngl

How to make your level goal look good:
Height should be 26, otherwise ending background will be one tile higher. Goal Roulette should be 8 tiles from right edge of the level and 5 tiles up from ground
Now you know that isn't a rip-off of an existing series called "the 8 worlds" Sewer?????????////// lmao i suck
